Validating Data Encryption in an HDFS Encryption Zone
To confirm that data in /secure_zone/myfile.txt is encrypted, follow these validation steps:

âœ” Check if /secure_zone is an Encryption Zone (EZ)
âœ” Verify that the file is encrypted in HDFS metadata
âœ” Check raw DataNode blocks to confirm encryption
âœ” Test unauthorized access to enforce security

ğŸ“Œ Step 1: Verify That /secure_zone Is an Encryption Zone
Run the following command:

bash
Copy
Edit
