âœ… Expected Output:

bash
Copy
Edit
/secure_zone my-secure-key
âœ” Confirms that /secure_zone is encrypted using my-secure-key.

ğŸ“Œ Step 2: Check File Metadata to Confirm Encryption
Run:

bash
Copy
Edit
