âœ” Confirms that only authorized users can access the encrypted data.

ğŸ“Œ Step 4: Locate Raw Data Blocks in HDFS DataNodes
To ensure that HDFS DataNodes store only encrypted data, find the raw block files.

1ï¸âƒ£ Find the Block ID of the File
bash
Copy
Edit
