âš  If plaintext data appears, encryption is NOT working correctly.

ğŸ“Œ Step 5: Try Accessing Raw Data Using the .reserved/raw Path
HDFS provides a hidden .reserved/raw path that allows accessing raw encrypted data.

Run:

bash
Copy
Edit
